file.name: strip-parent-name-nested-objects.yaml
file.content:
openapi: "3.0.0"
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: Strip Parent Name Nested Objects

paths:
  /container:
    get:
      responses:
        "200":
          description: ""
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/Container"
components:
  schemas:
    ContainerA:
      type: object
      properties:
        a:
          type: string
    ContainerB:
      type: object
      properties:
        b:
          type: string
    ContainerC:
      type: object
      properties:
        c:
          type: string

    Container:
      type: object
      required:
        - content
      properties:
        content:
          oneOf:
            - $ref: "#/components/schemas/ContainerA"
            - $ref: "#/components/schemas/ContainerB"
            - $ref: "#/components/schemas/ContainerC"
